# Venom Solutions Template Rules

## Template Scope

All UI and frontend changes must target `templates/venom-solutions/` only. Do not edit twenty-one, nexus, or other built-in templates.

## Page Context: Header & Footer

### Landing & Auth (`$useClientHeader = false`)

| Variable | Value |
|---------|-------|
| `$filename` | `index`, `login`, `register`, `pwreset` |
| Body class | `landing` |
| Header | `venom-header` (marketing nav) |
| Footer | `venom-footer` (full marketing footer) |

**Header content**: Logo, nav links (Home, Pricing, Login, Register), CTA.
**Footer content**: Brand, Quick Access, Support links, payment icons, copyright.

### Client Area (`$useClientHeader = true`)

| Variable | Value |
|---------|-------|
| `$loggedin` | true |
| Body class | `client-area` |
| Header | `venom-header venom-header-client` |
| Footer | `venom-client-footer` |

**Header content**: Logo + "Client Area" badge, notifications dropdown, cart, user menu, sidebar toggle.
**Footer content**: Copyright, payment chips, locale picker, back-to-top.

## Key Logic in header.tpl / footer.tpl

```smarty
{assign var=isAuthPage value=($filename eq 'login' or $filename eq 'register' or $filename eq 'pwreset')}
{assign var=isLandingPage value=($filename eq 'index')}
{assign var=useClientHeader value=($loggedin and not $isAuthPage and not $isLandingPage)}
```

## File Map

| Purpose | Path |
|---------|------|
| Shared styles | `css/venom-main.css` |
| Shared scripts | `js/venom-main.js` |
| Logo include | `includes/logo.tpl` |
| Auth pages | `login.tpl`, `clientregister.tpl`, `pwreset.tpl`, etc. |
| Client area | `clientareahome.tpl`, `clientareaproducts.tpl`, etc. |

## Do Not

- Add client-area UI (notifications, cart) to landing header.
- Add marketing footer (links, hero) to client area footer.
- Edit `twenty-one` or `nexus` for user-facing changes.
